<div class="inner" id="msg_1104687">Professional Rating 2 专业等级2<br>古人帮，切割者，索伦之子，万圣帮。这些名字比那些仅仅是随机暴力事件 (好吧，或许那是万圣帮令人恐惧的缘由) 还要恐怖的多。他们是专业的帮派组织，是要成为更强大的政党的一股更好战的武装力量。他们作战时间更长，但他们仍然不算老手。他们有着足够的自负和领袖，来让他们迫使自己保持战斗。<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Ancients. Cutters. Sons of Sauron. Halloweeners. These are names feared for something more than just random violence (well, maybe that’s exactly why the Halloweeners are feared). They are professional gangs and organizations designed to be the more militant arm of nicer policlubs. They’ve gotten more time under fire, but they’re still not pros, and they all have enough ego and rep that they push themselves a little harder to keep in the fight.</div></div></div> 索伦之子猛兽（兽人，已调整）Sons of Sauron Brute (Ork Adjustments Applied)<br>B A R S W L I C ESS DR I/ID AC CM MOVE<br>3 2 2 4 2 1 2 1 6 4 4/1 A1,I2 10 10/15/+1<br>技能：运动2 近身战斗4 枪械3 影响5（威吓+2）侦查3<br>装备：护甲外套（+2） 通讯链（设备等级2）<br>武器：伯莱塔101T【轻型手枪 DV2P SA 攻击等级9/8/6/-/-】<br>指虎【徒手 DV3P 攻击等级6/-/-/-/-】<br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTa